Hello,
	I have a couple of home grown patches for Fvwm 2.0.45 if anyone is
interested.

	One draws an outline around the title bar text.  I tend to use
fairly noisy title bar textures, and this makes the text infinitely more
readable.  Right now, it uses the background color for the outline, I am
working on allowing the user to specify a specific color for the outline.

	Window borders disappear now when I maximize a window.  The window
is truly maximized.

	Also, the title bar now extends for the entire width of the parent
frame, the side borders stop at the bottom of the title bar.  Also, there
is no top border (that is what the title bar is for).

	I can send screen shots if anyone is interested.

